<plot>Steve Fisher is a successful businessman. One hot summer day, he stops at a roadside lemonade stand. He purchases "Magic Lemonade" from the little girl who is running the stand. Steve drinks the lemonade and the secret ingredient makes him hallucinate. In return, he becomes addicted to it and craves more. As Steve keeps purchasing the "Magic Lemonade" the little girl starts to increase the price. Steve starts to steal money from work to buy the lemonade and is eventually fired. His wife leaves him, he loses his job and ends up homeless. Steve begs the little girl to tell him the magic ingredient. He eventually finds out what caused his life to fall apart.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?322024</url></doc>
